        "title": "How to debug SWT layout?",
        "body": "<p>I see excess space in a view. How to find, what is it there? Is there any debugging option or tool for layout managing?<\/p>\n\n<p>I have added <code>org.elipse.pde.picasso<\/code> plugin to my runtime config and set this plugin for tracing, but nothing happen visually.<\/p>\n\n<p>I there something like <code>debug<\/code> style in <code>MigLayout<\/code>?<\/p>\n",
