        "creation_date": 1489043128,
        "body": "<p>The Eclipse PDE Layout spy is a very nice tool to identify layout issues. If you have PDE installed, press Ctrl+Alt+Shift+F9 on any window to activate it.  See <a href=\"http://www.vogella.com/tutorials/EclipsePlatformDevelopment/article.html#layout-spy\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">http://www.vogella.com/tutorials/EclipsePlatformDevelopment/article.html#layout-spy<\/a> for more information.<\/p>\n",
